('Ruby Reverie', 'https://i.ibb.co/4WwZcHc/ruby-reverie.jpg', 'The Ruby Reverie bracelet is a captivating blend of timeless elegance and bold sophistication. Featuring alternating oval-cut rubies and dazzling diamonds set in warm yellow gold, this bracelet embodies the perfect balance of luxury and charm. Its striking design evokes passion and confidence, making it a stunning statement piece for any occasion.', ARRAY['18k yellow gold', 'Alternating oval-cut rubies and round diamonds', 'Length: 7 inches', 'Designed for comfort and secure wear', 'Product number: 70183912'], '$39,000');
