('Rose Quartz Elegance', 'https://i.ibb.co/YTk8P5P/rose-quartz-elegance.jpg', 'The Rose Quartz Elegance watch offers a touch of femininity and luxury. With its rose gold case, pearl-white dial, and diamond accents, this timepiece is both delicate and dazzling. The perfect blend of sophistication and practicality, it’s ideal for the modern woman.', ARRAY['Rose gold case and band', 'Pearl-white dial with diamond markers', 'Quartz movement', 'Diameter: 32mm', 'Product number: 80112002'], '$3,400');
